org.sql: SELECT spree_variants.* FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_variants.product_id = spree_products.id INNER JOIN spree_products_stores ON spree_products.id = spree_products_stores.product_id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_products_stores.store_id = "$1" ORDER BY spree_variants.position ASC

rewrites.sql: SELECT spree_variants.* FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_variants.product_id = spree_products.id INNER JOIN spree_products_stores ON spree_products.id = spree_products_stores.product_id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_products_stores.store_id = "$1" ORDER BY spree_variants.position ASC LIMIT 1
